# Coursework / scratch PDFs that accidentally end up in the static-assets
# folder. The deployed PDFs are GENERATED at request time by app/reporting.py,
# so we never need to commit a PDF here. If a PDF needs to ship, drop it under
# app/static/case-studies/ instead.
app/static/assets/*.pdf

